"The paper trading refresh completed successfully. Let me provide a summary to the user.\\n\\nKey findings:\\n1. The paper trading ran successfully for 20260407\\n2. Status: PASS\\n3. The strategy is in \\\"cautious\\\" mode with halt_new_buy=true\\n4. The main halt reason is: strategy_max_drawdown_pct(23.31%) >= 10.0000% threshold\\n5. Also triggered liquidity_riskoff\\n6. Market breadth: 0.74 (high)\\n7. Index return (ZZ2000): +2.35%\\n\\nThe drawdown is quite high at 23.31%, which is why it's in risk-off mode. This is interesting because the index went up 2.35% today.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"模拟盘已刷新 ✅\\n\\n**2026-04-07 运行结果：PASS**\\n\\n| 项目 | 值 |\\n|------|-----|\\n| 状态 | 通过 |\\n| 模式 | **cautious**（谨慎模式） |\\n| 新开仓 | 🚫 已暂停 |\\n| 原因 | 策略历史最大回撤 23.31% > 阈值 10% |\\n| 市场宽度 | 0.74（偏高） |\\n| ZZ2000涨跌 | +2.35% |\\n\\n市场今天涨了 2.35%，但策略因为历史回撤超标仍处于风控锁仓状态，不会下新单。现有持仓会继续被动管理（止损/止盈）。\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775551834819,\n      \"responseId\": \"0623f85b0654c07731416181aa0645a3\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"dbeae9a1\",\n        \"seq\": 96\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"张玲: [Replying to: \\\"[Interactive Card]\\\"]\\n\\n这个逻辑不对，不能因为超过了最大回撤就暂停开仓\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1775552021205,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"740a66cc\",\n        \"seq\": 97\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775552021211,\n      \"responseId\": \"\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"36fcab5b\",\n        \"seq\": 98\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"张玲: [Replying to: \\\"好，做方案 B。这个重构涉及以下核心文件：\\n主要改动：\\n\\\\- generate\\\\_live\\\\_smallcap\\\\_candidates.py — 价格源从 CSV → 盘中实时 API\\n\\\\- run\\\\_live\\\\_system\\\\_v1.py — 切换盘中/盘后价格路由\\n\\\\- 可能新增 fetch\\\\_realtime\\\\_prices.py — 封装腾讯/新浪实时价格拉取逻辑\\n主要改动点：\\n1. 加 \\\\-\\\\-realtime / \\\\-\\\\-eod 模式 flag\\n2. 盘中用腾讯/新浪 API 拿当前价（而非 CSV 里的昨日收盘价）\\n3. 信号逻辑不变，但价格输入变成实时流\\n4. 盘后（18:00 后）自动回退到 CSV 日线，正常衔接\\n风险提示：\\n\\\\- 实时价格有 bid/ask spread，不同期权数据源可能有微小差异\\n\\\\- 盘中信号会比 EOD 信号波动更大（这是真实的，不是 bug）\\n\\\\- 策略的参数（阈值、权重）可能需要根据盘中特性重新调\\n这个需要 1\\\\-2 小时开发和测试。我现在开始拆解代码、找齐需要改的函数，做好之后手动验证再给你看结果。完成后会通知你。\\\"]\\n\\n完成了吗\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1775552579432,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"6ec1507b\",\n        \"seq\": 99\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Two different conversations:\\n1. 关于模拟盘逻辑的反馈 - 说\\\"不能因为超过了最大回撤就暂停开仓\\\"，这是在回复我之前说的 cautel mode 原因\\n2. 问方案B的实时价格重构完成了吗\\n\\nLet me check on both. First, let me check if there's been progress on the realtime price system, and also look at the paper trading config to understand the max drawdown halt logic issue.\\n\\nFor question 1: The user says the logic is wrong - we shouldn't halt new buys just because strategy max drawdown exceeds threshold. This is the `strategy_max_drawdown_pct(23.3100) >= 10.0000` gate reason. This is a valid point - max drawdown is a historical metric, not a current drawdown metric. Halting new buys based on historical max drawdown doesn't make sense.\\n \\nFor question 2: The realtime price work is still in progress and hasn't been completed yet.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"\\n\\n\\n**两件事：**\\n\\n**1. 模拟盘逻辑 — 你是对的，这个逻辑确实有问题。**\\n\\n`strategy_max_drawdown_pct(23.31%) >= 10%` 是**历史最大回撤**，不是当前持仓的实时浮亏。用它来 halt 新开仓不合理——历史最大回撤只说明\\\"这个策略在过去最惨的时候跌过多少\\\"，不应该成为今天是否下单的依据。\\n\\n我需要把 `strategy_sharpe_cautious_threshold` 和相关 halt 规则梳理清楚，改成用**当前实时回撤**或**实时风险指标**来驱动风控，而不是历史 max drawdown。\\n\\n**2. 方案B（实时价格）** — 还没完成，还在开发中。刚才那个 session 因为上下文切换被中断了。我应该继续让它跑完，但现在的 coding agent session 被我的心跳检查打断了。\\n\\n你想让我现在继续推方案B的开发，还是先集中改模拟盘的 halt 逻辑？\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775552579440,\n      \"responseId\": \"0623fb43c994115918053bf3de333aaf\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"88517364\",\n        \"seq\": 100\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"张玲: 继续推方案B\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1775552951523,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"574991fa\",\n        \"seq\": 101\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775552951530,\n      \"responseId\": \"\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"825e0563\",\n        \"seq\": 102\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"现在改模拟盘逻辑\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1775554575791,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"dafc4519\",\n        \"seq\": 103\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n  