{"type":"message","id":"cc0155e9","parentId":"4bc874a0","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:37:53.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So v4_3 is NOT registered in the panel_profile_registry at all! That's the problem. The `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG` in `panel_profile_registry.py` doesn't have an entry for `v4_3` or `smallcap_chip_v4_3_aggressive`. So it falls back to default thresholds:\n- `riskoff_pct = cfg.get(\"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\", 10.0)` → 10.0 (default)\n- `halt_pct = cfg.get(\"strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct\", 15.0)` → 15.0 (default)\n\n\nSince there's no metrics file for v4_3 either, the current drawdown is 23.31% from the global live system, which exceeds the 10.0 riskoff threshold and 15.0 halt threshold, triggering both risk-off and halt conditions. I need to look at the panel_profile_registry to see how other profiles are configured and what's missing for v4_3.","thinkingSignature":"81457078618d0eeb69f53f1f3644ea3603fbbe4fd5120a941ba2de83ed61aa6a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5rxr33sx3dt2_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/panel_profile_registry.py","limit":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":46033,"output":273,"cacheRead":23779,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70085,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775554666155,"responseId":"0624036aeb01da3862d9f50c8e638557"}}
{"type":"message","id":"322ad47f","parentId":"cc0155e9","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:37:53.662Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5rxr33sx3dt2_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"from __future__ import annotations\n\nfrom typing import Any\n\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Panel-level runtime risk truth configuration\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 三盘重构核心：每盘使用独立的 runtime risk truth source，不再共享全局 halt。\n# 关键字段说明：\n#   strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct : 本盘允许的最大回撤阈值（触发 risk_off）\n#   strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct    : 本盘的硬停阈值（触发 halt_new_buy）\n#   halt_gate_source                   : 本盘的 halt gate 来源文件路径模板\n#   candidate_source_tag               : 本盘使用的候选股来源标签\n#   probe_budget_tag                   : 本盘使用的探测预算标签\n#\n# 当前全局风险真相（20260331）：strategy_max_drawdown_pct=24.51%，halt_new_buy=true\n# 三盘分层目标（首轮）：\n#   aggressive : strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct=30%, halt_pct=35%  （容忍最高回撤）\n#   balanced   : strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct=22%, halt_pct=28%\n#   defensive  : strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct=10%, halt_pct=15%  （与原全局一致）\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG: dict[str, dict[str, Any]] = {\n    \"aggressive\": {\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\": 30.0,\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct\": 35.0,\n        \"halt_gate_source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest_aggressive.json\",\n        \"candidate_source_tag\": \"aggressive_high_elasticity\",\n        \"probe_budget_tag\": \"probe_budget_high\",\n        \"risk_off_exposure_cap\": 0.85,\n        \"hard_stop_enabled\": True,\n    },\n    \"balanced\": {\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\": 22.0,\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct\": 28.0,\n        \"halt_gate_source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest_balanced.json\",\n        \"candidate_source_tag\": \"balanced_mid_quality\",\n        \"probe_budget_tag\": \"probe_budget_mid\",\n        \"risk_off_exposure_cap\": 0.70,\n        \"hard_stop_enabled\": True,\n    },\n    \"defensive\": {\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\": 10.0,\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct\": 15.0,\n        \"halt_gate_source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json\",\n        \"candidate_source_tag\": \"defensive_top_quality\",\n        \"probe_budget_tag\": \"probe_budget_low\",\n        \"risk_off_exposure_cap\": 0.55,\n        \"hard_stop_enabled\": True,\n    },\n}\n\n\ndef profile_runtime_risk_config(profile_slug: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Return the panel-level runtime risk config for a given profile slug.\n\n    Returns a copy so callers can mutate without affecting the registry.\n    Falls back to the defensive defaults if the slug is not found.\n    \"\"\"\n    default_cfg = PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG.get(\"defensive\", {})\n\n[100 more lines in file. Use offset=61 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775554673657}}
{"type":"message","id":"58f54b3f","parentId":"322ad47f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:38:15.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture. The `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG` only has entries for `aggressive`, `balanced`, and `defensive`. The v4.3 profile (`smallcap_chip_v4_3_aggressive`) is NOT registered here.\n\nLooking at the current situation:\n1. v4.3 paper profile started today (20260407), first day of trading\n2. No metrics file yet → `get_paper_real_drawdown()` returns `None`\n3. Profile not in `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG` → uses defaults: riskoff_pct=10%, halt_pct=15%\n4. Falls back to live_system global metrics: strategy_max_dd_pct = 23.31%\n\n\n5. Since 23.31% > 10% riskoff threshold → triggers risk_off and halt_new_buy\n\nBut here's the real issue: the 23.31% max drawdown comes from the live system's 11-year out-of-sample backtest on the old strategy, not the v4.3 parameters that were only deployed to paper trading today. The old aggressive profile had its own max drawdown settings of 30% riskoff and 35% halt, so using v4.3's 10%/15% thresholds against the old strategy's metrics is a complete mismatch. What's needed is either to register v4_3 in the config with appropriate thresholds, or better yet, track paper trading metrics from day one so we can use the actual drawdown from the current strategy instead of relying on historical backtest data.\n\nFor v4.3's paper trading, since it literally started today with a fresh million dollars and zero holdings, the real max drawdown should be 0% or near zero depending on how the metrics are being calculated. I need to figure out where the 23.31% is actually coming from and whether it's being incorrectly applied to this new profile.\n\nLooking at the code flow, when there's no metrics file yet, it falls back to the live system's out-of-sample max drawdown of 23.31%, which shouldn't be used for a brand new paper portfolio. The solution is to either register v4.3 in the panel profile registry with its own thresholds, or adjust the logic so it doesn't apply the live system's historical drawdown to a fresh start.\n\nExamining the halt condition more closely, I see it's checking if current drawdown exceeds 10%, but this is the historical out-of-sample drawdown from the live system, not the actual paper trading performance. Since v4.3 is a new profile that just started paper trading today, there's no meaningful drawdown to evaluate against these thresholds yet.\n\nThe better approach would be to either set the drawdown thresholds higher for this new profile (like 35-40% to match its live trading counterpart) so it doesn't trigger halt on day one, or skip the halt check entirely until actual paper trading metrics exist. I'm leaning toward adjusting the thresholds since that's the more robust solution, though I need to verify what the current thresholds actually are before changing them.","thinkingSignature":"75dae9815ba991252b5e3d7a636a22c6799b962859433d6c62f5352b11f826db"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bkn56t9btgy5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"v4_3\\|smallcap_chip\\|breadth_aggressive\\|breadth_strict\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/panel_profile_registry.py 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bkn56t9btgy5_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"profile_slug\\|v4_3\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":47019,"output":781,"cacheRead":23779,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71579,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775554673663,"responseId":"06240372136f4e24130f00cb73315500"}}
