{"type":"message","id":"71261a49","parentId":"6538a1ea","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:40:26.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `profile_slug` is `v4_3_aggressive`. So the slug used in the system is `v4_3_aggressive`, not `smallcap_chip_v4_3_aggressive`.\n\nNow let me check if `v4_3_aggressive` is in `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG`.\n\nCurrently:- `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG` has: `aggressive`, `balanced`, `defensive`, `exit_dual`, `exit_tight`, `alpha55`, `breadth_strict_oos`, `breadth_aggressive`\n- `v4_3_aggressive` is NOT in the list → falls back to defensive defaults (10%/15%)\n\n\n- The old `aggressive` profile uses 30%/35%, but `v4_3_aggressive` should be treated as its own distinct profile since it has different OOS metrics. Since there's no metrics file for `v4_3_aggressive` yet, it would fall back to the live_system's OOS max drawdown of 23.31%, which exceeds the 10% threshold and triggers halt.\n\nI need to add `v4_3_aggressive` to the `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG` and `CURRENT_PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS` with appropriate risk thresholds, then check if `PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS` also needs to be updated to include it.","thinkingSignature":"64e4bf667ec657f1b29f0d8a66f00f9e2a5b623b54b6f27d26357d2a37aa347b"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了。profile_slug 是 `v4_3_aggressive`，但它根本没有注册进 `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG`，所以用的是防御级阈值（10%/15%硬停），而回退数据是 live_system OOS 的 23.31%，直接超过阈值导致 halt。\n\n**修复方案：** 把 `v4_3_aggressive` 注册进 `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG`（用进取型阈值 30%/35%），并加入 `CURRENT_PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS`：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2wecbf1t55l1_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/panel_profile_registry.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    \"defensive\": {\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\": 10.0,\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct\": 15.0,\n        \"halt_gate_source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json\",\n        \"can