{"type":"message","id":"71c2b3c4","parentId":"8ec5eff1","timestamp":"2026-04-07T11:00:20.140Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script ran but many profiles failed because of \"stale_price_source\" - the market trade date is 20260331 (7 days lag). This is a data issue, not a logic issue. But importantly, the script didn't block due to halt_new_buy now.\n\nLet me summarize what was done and explain to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"74c02647c98b780cec722bfd4864a4e321966a7bc267661be1f61df2989cef6f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n模拟盘逻辑修复完成 ✅\n\n**修复内容：**\n\n1. **panel_profile_registry.py** — 添加了 v4.3 纸盘的独立风险阈值配置（riskoff=30%, halt=35%）\n\n2. **run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh** — 不再被实盘 halt 逻辑阻断，纸盘使用自己的 per-panel 风险判断\n\n3. **generate_per_panel_runtime_risk_t05.py** — 新增 v4_3_aggressive 面板\n\n**验证结果：**\n\n```\nv4_3_aggressive: halt=False, risk_off=False, halt_pct=35.0%, paper_dd=23.31%\n```\n\n今天 v4.3 纸盘的 halt 已解除，可以正常交易。\n\n---\n\n⚠️ **注意：** 刚才运行时多个纸盘失败，原因是 **价格数据滞后 7 天**（20260331）：\n- `stale_price_source: market_trade_date=20260331 lag_days=7`\n\n这会导致候选股无法生成。需要更新 `a_stock_history.csv` 数据源才能正常执行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1610,"output":300,"cacheRead":80768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82678,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775559604272,"responseId":"062416b490f2a2ebd62b48890532f110"}}
